# 1. Front-Facing Website Skeleton

## Purpose

The front-facing website is the **public commercial and explanatory surface**. It must:
- explain the platform
- package products, memberships, offers, and resources
- support lead capture and enquiry
- support DocuShare and product entry points
- route users into sign-in, registration, booking, or purchase pathways

## Primary routes

```text
/
/home
/docushare
/applications
/membership
/offers
/resources
/help
/contact
/sign-in
/register
/forgot-password
/reset-password
/auth/callback
```

