# 7. What Must Be Mocked vs What Must Be Defined

## Safe to mock in AI Studio
- page copy
- sample cards
- placeholder tables
- KPI widgets
- alert banners
- fake notices
- empty-state content
- module tiles and status examples
- example invoices/receipts/resources/documents

## Must be defined conceptually before or during build
- route model
- surface separation
- navigation groups
- major screen purposes
- state vocabulary
- user-role assumptions
- module catalogue categories
- launch method vocabulary

## Must not be faked into permanent product logic
- real entitlements
- real billing logic
- real access decisions
- real onboarding/compliance decisions
- real SSO/session logic
- real repository launch governance

